Posts.Content: Dont be concerned. This happens to lots of women and not only in the breast....you can feel this vibrating/buzzing feeling anywhere.   Its thought to be a tiny spasm of underlying muscles.....like the twitching you can get near the eye,and often associated with being overtired or a bit stressed. Try to get a few early nights. Report Reply
